{"tid":574064,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"asus ac68u router問題","createTime":"2018-02-27T05:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T06:03:55.000Z","uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f40ece02d456fa0ab198ffe97034aab3db59abf","tid":574064,"uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"因為依排覺得個速度有慢左 測完速度先知原來真係慢左<br />\n本身用緊500mb plan 近排發現download得返3xx mb左右 upload就無問題<br />\n<br />\n已知:<br />\n1) 唔經router直插直頭超過500mb download速度<br />\n2) Reset 成個router會超過500mb download速度<br />\n<br />\n咁應該得出係router有問題/router setting有問題<br />\n之前上年有果個WannaCry 搞到要封Port防一防<br />\n咁我都有係router到set 我就封左以下既port<br />\n139\t\t\tTCP\t<br />\n445\t\t\tTCP\t<br />\n139\t\t\tUDP\t<br />\n445\t\t\tUDP\t<br />\n3389\t\tTCP\t<br />\n137\t\t\tTCP\t<br />\n138\t\t\tTCP<br />\n求巴打解答我應該點做先有返高d既速度而又防到d port無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac434f1b20a6de9dbee9a50b563d7ea39b5383ed","tid":574064,"uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T07:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe43006cd723e5d86d0f1dba73c031cc52404a10","tid":574064,"uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T09:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349f03a6963d899338710a04d6e8a2140791090c","tid":574064,"uid":19520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"